                    "shum": "Kamm nimf? Zasiba.",
                    "english": "How are you? I’m in well-being.",
                    "explanation": "Where’s your awareness? In harmony.",
                    "audio": "/audio/lesson1/Kamm-nimf-Zasiba.m4a"
                },
                {
                    "shum": "Tyebabalingna, dikamaja!",
                    "english": "Happy feelings, goodbye!",
